      "start": 28,
      "end": 46,
      "html": "<section class=\"slide eq\"><ul class=\"eq-lines\"><li id=\"implyzvcj2m\" class=\" eq-item eq-title \" > Testing with Numbers </li><li id=\"implyzvcj2n\" class=\" eq-item eq-math \" > $$ (2+3)^2 $$ </li><li id=\"implyzvcj2o\" class=\" eq-item eq-math \" > $$ = 4 + 6 + 6 + 9 $$ </li><li id=\"implyzvcj2p\" class=\" eq-item eq-math \" > $$ = 25 $$ </li><li id=\"implyzvcj2q\" class=\" eq-item eq-line \" > Verification improves confidence. </li></ul><div class=\"eq-side-panel\"><div id=\"implyzvcj2m-sp-1\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" ><img src=\"image.png\" /></div><div id=\"implyzvcj2m-sp-2\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > The same structure works numerically. </div><div id=\"implyzvcj2m-sp-3\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > Substitute values into the identity. </div><div id=\"implyzvcj2m-sp-4\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > (2+3)^2 </div><div id=\"implyzvcj2m-sp-5\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > Now expand step by step. </div><div id=\"implyzvcj2n-sp-1\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" ><img src=\"eq.webp\" /></div><div id=\"implyzvcj2n-sp-2\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > The bracket multiplies itself. </div><div id=\"implyzvcj2n-sp-3\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > (2+3)(2+3) </div><div id=\"implyzvcj2n-sp-4\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > Repeated multiplication begins. </div><div id=\"implyzvcj2n-sp-5\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > Every term interacts. </div><div id=\"implyzvcj2o-sp-1\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" ><img src=\"box.webp\" /></div><div id=\"implyzvcj2o-sp-2\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > 2\\times2=4 </div><div id=\"implyzvcj2o-sp-3\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > 2\\times3=6 </div><div id=\"implyzvcj2o-sp-4\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > 3\\times2=6 </div><div id=\"implyzvcj2o-sp-5\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > 3\\times3=9 </div><div id=\"implyzvcj2o-sp-6\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > All products are visible separately. </div><div id=\"implyzvcj2p-sp-1\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" ><img src=\"force-intro.webp\" /></div><div id=\"implyzvcj2p-sp-2\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > Add all values carefully. </div><div id=\"implyzvcj2p-sp-3\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > 4+6+6+9=25 </div><div id=\"implyzvcj2p-sp-4\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > The identity works correctly. </div><div id=\"implyzvcj2p-sp-5\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > Expansion and simplification agree. </div><div id=\"implyzvcj2q-sp-1\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" ><img src=\"image.png\" /></div><div id=\"implyzvcj2q-sp-2\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > Students trust identities more after testing. </div><div id=\"implyzvcj2q-sp-3\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > Concrete numbers reduce abstraction. </div><div id=\"implyzvcj2q-sp-4\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > Patterns become easier to recognize. </div></div></section>",
